39:04.925 --> 39:06.260
Whoa, ma'am, ma'am, ma'am!

39:06.344 --> 39:09.930
Who are you? You can't go in there!

39:10.473 --> 39:11.849
Uh, you see, I--

39:12.725 --> 39:15.186
I just saw my daughter.
She was walking that way.

39:16.020 --> 39:19.023
-Your daughter?
-She, uh-- She just walked in.

39:19.106 --> 39:20.858
She-- She was wearing a denim skirt

39:20.941 --> 39:23.277
and long shoes
that come up to here, you know?

39:23.361 --> 39:24.278
Denim?

39:25.237 --> 39:27.740
-Ah, Mi-ae.
-"Mi-ae"?

39:27.823 --> 39:31.577
Uh-huh. When she's out, I'll tell her
you came by. She's busy at the moment.

39:31.660 --> 39:33.537
Not right now. Bye now. Here.

39:33.621 --> 39:34.955
-Wait. Wait a minute.
-Huh?

39:35.039 --> 39:36.374
Please don't tell her

39:36.457 --> 39:38.292
that I came by, is that okay?

39:38.376 --> 39:42.546
I-- If she finds out I came here,
my-- my daughter will be furious.

39:43.047 --> 39:44.423
-You know her.
-Right.

39:44.507 --> 39:47.051
How would she feel
knowing that her mom knows she works here?

39:47.134 --> 39:49.637
-Okay, ma'am, I understand. Go now!
-Right.

39:49.720 --> 39:50.554
Uh-huh. Go on.

39:50.638 --> 39:53.349
-Not a word.
-Of course, not a word.

39:53.849 --> 39:55.935
-Mi-ae.
-Yeah, Mi-ae, Mi-ae. Uh-huh.

39:56.018 --> 40:00.231
Bye now, ma'am. Bye. Goodbye!

40:23.379 --> 40:24.964
Hey! What are you doing?!

40:59.790 --> 41:02.460
Mom! Save me, please!

41:05.921 --> 41:07.339
Oh-nam!

41:11.260 --> 41:12.428
Oh-nam!

41:20.561 --> 41:22.938
Oh-nam!

41:30.863 --> 41:32.072
Mom.

41:35.868 --> 41:38.204
You didn't save me. Why didn't you, huh?

41:41.290 --> 41:42.458
I'm sorry.

41:43.667 --> 41:45.669
You were embarrassed of me, weren't you?

41:47.296 --> 41:48.797
What are you saying?

41:52.343 --> 41:54.220
I couldn't get into medical school,

41:54.303 --> 41:57.181
and I never dated anyone,
so you were embarrassed of me!

41:57.264 --> 41:58.891
You actually wanted me to die!

41:58.974 --> 42:01.644
No! No!

42:01.727 --> 42:03.479
That's not true.

42:04.813 --> 42:06.815
You're glad I'm dead!

42:07.316 --> 42:09.068
I'm sorry, son--

42:10.152 --> 42:11.445
I'm sorry…

42:16.158 --> 42:17.076
Scuse me.

42:18.244 --> 42:19.286
Are you all right?

42:21.163 --> 42:22.665
Ma-am, hey!

44:15.152 --> 44:18.656
You're always being judgmental. Hmm?

44:18.739 --> 44:19.990
-Welcome!
-Welcome!

44:20.824 --> 44:24.536
-How can I help you?
-I'm here to, uh, get my hair done.

44:24.620 --> 44:27.331
Oh. Are you looking
for a specific hairdresser?

44:28.415 --> 44:30.417
What dresser? Just do my hair.

44:31.502 --> 44:34.755
-Yeah, so he went home, just like that.
-Oh my gosh, that's crazy.

44:34.838 --> 44:37.383
Wow, he's such a jerk!
Like, just, wow!

44:37.466 --> 44:40.386
He's gotta be crazy, I mean…
You know what?

44:40.469 --> 44:42.304
I think that jerk is ghosting you.

44:42.388 --> 44:44.223
I'm the crazy one.

44:44.306 --> 44:46.642
He's so annoying!
Why did I ever agree to this?

44:46.725 --> 44:48.686
Let's go wash your hair, shall we?

44:49.269 --> 44:52.690
He said he was a genius,
and I totally fell for it. Damn it.

44:52.773 --> 44:54.233
Oh, forget him.

44:55.859 --> 44:58.237
Hello, ma'am. What look are you going for?

44:58.946 --> 45:01.448
I, uh, wanna wash my hair first.

45:01.532 --> 45:02.366
Sure.

45:03.826 --> 45:05.285
Please have a seat over here.

45:07.996 --> 45:09.498
Hold on just a sec.

45:15.921 --> 45:17.756
All right, you can lie down, please.

45:21.760 --> 45:24.847
I think I've seen that necklace before.

45:26.098 --> 45:27.057
Where did I see it?

45:33.439 --> 45:34.773
USB DEVICE RECOGNIZED

45:43.407 --> 45:44.241
MASK GIRL

46:02.259 --> 46:03.177
Found it.

46:04.470 --> 46:05.721
I finally found it.

46:11.769 --> 46:13.771
MASK GIRL ♥ TEDDY REQUESTS A 1:1 CHAT

46:13.854 --> 46:15.898
MASK GIRL ♥ TEDDY: MG LOVE,
HOW HAVE YOU BEEN?

46:15.981 --> 46:17.316
What do you think?

46:19.777 --> 46:22.279
MG LOVE: JUST SO-SO.

46:22.362 --> 46:23.906
MASK GIRL ♥ TEDDY: DON'T BE FREAKED OUT!

46:25.574 --> 46:26.617
I'M IN GANGCHEON

46:26.700 --> 46:27.701
Hm?

46:33.624 --> 46:35.417
MASK GIRL ♥ TEDDY: I'VE BEEN THINKING...

46:35.501 --> 46:37.544
I THINK THAT WOMAN REALLY IS MASK GIRL!

46:37.628 --> 46:38.837
MG LOVE: REALLY?

46:38.921 --> 46:40.881
MASK GIRL ♥ TEDDY:
I WENT TO THE SUPERMARKET IN THE VIDEO

46:42.633 --> 46:44.635
APPARENTLY, HER MOM

46:44.718 --> 46:47.012
WAS LOOKING FOR HER IN GANGCHEON!

46:47.095 --> 46:48.680
CONSIDERING ALL THAT

46:48.764 --> 46:52.226
I THINK SHE'S REALLY MASK GIRL, BUT…

46:52.309 --> 46:54.311
What does he think he is, a detective?

47:02.569 --> 47:03.737
TAXICAB DRIVER'S LICENSE
KYUNG-JA KIM

47:03.821 --> 47:06.907
Wow! You got this license
a long time ago, huh?

47:07.658 --> 47:09.243
Are you sure you can handle it?

47:10.410 --> 47:12.788
-Aren't you too old?
-Don't worry about it.

47:13.413 --> 47:15.040
I know the gas and brake pedal.

47:41.358 --> 47:42.484
I'm here to buy a gun.

47:43.944 --> 47:45.529
You're the lady who called us?

47:46.697 --> 47:49.324
Shit! Just my luck.

47:51.451 --> 47:53.412
I heard it's three million won.

47:55.163 --> 47:56.164
Here's ten million.

48:04.715 --> 48:08.760
This one. This is a Glock.
Straight from Austria. Eh?

48:10.304 --> 48:12.347
For a madam like you,
though, this is too, uh--

48:12.431 --> 48:13.265
Forget that.

48:13.891 --> 48:15.517
I want the most powerful one.

48:17.394 --> 48:19.396
The most powerful one?

48:21.231 --> 48:22.357
This one.

48:25.611 --> 48:26.445
Hmm?

48:32.743 --> 48:34.286
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

48:34.369 --> 48:35.370
This is good enough.

48:45.255 --> 48:47.507
In you go!

48:47.591 --> 48:49.468
Oh, come on.

48:49.551 --> 48:52.429
Get in the taxi behind me.
I'm not working tonight.

48:52.512 --> 48:55.474
-Damn it. What the hell, seriously?!
-Come on!

48:55.557 --> 48:57.225
Come on.

48:58.936 --> 49:00.771
C'mon, let's go home.

49:02.606 --> 49:05.817
VACANT

49:23.585 --> 49:26.797
Uh, you must be exhausted
from working so late, huh?

49:27.589 --> 49:28.924
Oh. Yeah.

49:29.007 --> 49:31.259
You know, you look
about my daughter's age.

49:32.928 --> 49:33.845
How old are you?

49:34.721 --> 49:36.223
I'm 28.

49:36.306 --> 49:38.600
Wow. You're the same age as her.

49:38.684 --> 49:39.685
As my daughter.

49:41.812 --> 49:43.605
Is that so?

49:57.494 --> 49:59.162
Excuse me, miss.

50:00.580 --> 50:03.208
My phone fell under the seat
in front you here.

50:03.291 --> 50:05.127
Could you pick it up for me?

50:05.210 --> 50:07.212
Yeah.

50:10.507 --> 50:11.591
I can't find it.

50:12.175 --> 50:14.094
-Is it not there?
-Where is it?

50:14.636 --> 50:17.681
-I don't see it.
-Oh. It's right here. It's here.

50:17.764 --> 50:19.016
What?

51:17.741 --> 51:18.992
Awake, are you?

51:34.341 --> 51:36.843
Somebody help! Help!

51:37.344 --> 51:40.347
-Please, anyone! Help!
-Help, please!

51:40.430 --> 51:43.141
Help!

51:50.440 --> 51:54.277
What's the matter with you?
Why are you doing this? Who are you?

52:02.869 --> 52:04.079
You don't know who I am?

52:04.663 --> 52:06.039
I really don't.

52:07.374 --> 52:09.543
I have no idea!
Why the hell are you doing this?

52:15.715 --> 52:19.094
Wait, ma'am, ma'am.
Wait. Please, wait a minute.

52:20.011 --> 52:21.263
I'm sorry.

52:23.181 --> 52:24.850
I don't know what I did wrong,

52:26.184 --> 52:27.727
but I'll do anything you want.

52:33.150 --> 52:35.110
You're back to your senses, apparently.

52:44.911 --> 52:45.912
Who is that person?

52:50.208 --> 52:51.251
You don't know him?

52:53.295 --> 52:54.379
You little…

52:54.462 --> 52:55.755
Ma'am!

52:55.839 --> 52:58.383
I don't know him, I swear to you!

52:59.134 --> 53:01.928
I've never seen this man
in my life!

53:03.305 --> 53:04.764
I do know who you are.

53:05.682 --> 53:06.766
Your real name

53:07.559 --> 53:08.643
is Mo-mi Kim.

53:08.727 --> 53:10.854
Mo-mi Kim?

53:11.771 --> 53:14.274
What do you mean?
I'm Chun-ae Kim! You're wrong!

53:15.150 --> 53:16.818
"Chun-ae Kim," huh?

53:17.319 --> 53:18.361
What a tacky name.

53:19.362 --> 53:21.865
So how many names do you have?

53:21.948 --> 53:24.117
Right…

53:25.702 --> 53:26.912
Is this not you?

53:27.537 --> 53:28.830
Yu-mi Choi?

53:30.123 --> 53:31.499
How did you get this?

53:34.085 --> 53:35.837
Do you still feel like lying?

53:36.421 --> 53:38.882
-I'm telling the truth!
-You damn bitch!

53:42.719 --> 53:45.305
Stay still or I'll stomp
all over your face.

53:52.103 --> 53:53.563
Wh-- What's the mask for?

53:56.399 --> 53:57.317
Ma'am?

53:57.984 --> 53:59.277
Why are you doing this?

53:59.819 --> 54:01.446
It's really not me.

54:01.947 --> 54:04.282
Please… Please don't do this.

54:05.408 --> 54:07.702
I've never heard
of the name Mo-mi Kim before.

54:07.786 --> 54:10.789
You lie
every time you open your mouth, you bitch.

54:10.872 --> 54:12.707
Now that I see you like this,
I'm sure of it.

54:12.791 --> 54:15.877
-It's really not me.
-It's you. It is you!

54:18.171 --> 54:21.383
Ma'am, I'm telling you,
it's really not me.

54:25.470 --> 54:26.930
Why are you doing this?

54:27.013 --> 54:28.723
You wore that mask

54:29.641 --> 54:31.726
when you killed my son, didn't you?

54:32.602 --> 54:36.606
Ma'am, why would I kill your son?
It wasn't me! I swear it wasn't me!

54:36.690 --> 54:39.276
I've never seen your son in my life,
I swear to God!

54:39.359 --> 54:41.319
I've looked at your photos

54:41.403 --> 54:43.989
as many times as I've looked at my son's.

54:45.699 --> 54:48.910
The necklace you're wearing,

54:49.828 --> 54:52.205
it's the same as the one in the picture.

54:53.415 --> 54:55.125
Necklace?

55:12.517 --> 55:15.645
Are you going crazy now, bitch?

55:21.234 --> 55:24.237
I think--
I think I know who that girl is.

55:25.488 --> 55:26.406
What?!

55:30.076 --> 55:32.245
You said her name's Mo-mi Kim, didn't you?

